{"type": "article", "id": 59697, "title": "爱奇艺会员费超过了广告费，肯德基和“知否”做酥饼 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-26T04:17:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5503, "name": "新年"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 9240, "name": "MINI"}], "category": 18, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181226120213Q6toxdJSmrvpPswV.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p line=\"TfV0\">肯德基和电视剧“知否知否应是绿肥红瘦”推出新品<a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/50089934.html?weibo_id=4321205777434815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>玫瑰酥饼</b></a>，将于 12 月 31 日登陆肯德基甜品站，限量发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a0818qlunul\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"iAya\">京东互联网医院成立 1 周年之际，推出“1元问诊”的活动。同时上线 H5<b><a href=\"http://h5.whalesgeek.net/cp/jd_hlwyy/index.html?adtag=wx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> “奇怪朋友圈调查所”</a>，</b>看看当下年轻人都有哪些身体问题，传达健康永远是最重要的事。由鲸梦文化制作。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115119JhAIxFj4SQHn8uBc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028065\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115120uIg9jDbORfqk3ZaT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028065\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115121KEO2YH3yUvWp0gDX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028065\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115121FSWqvtalNZpTUBEA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028065\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115122Mi6hRIjJ9u2ZbdNk.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028065\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Sz7F\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NjAxMzM2Mg==&amp;mid=2750274893&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=547a4fbfd348dbe4446b81d347c6c513&amp;chksm=cdfa1f90fa8d9686750966fa90b7166f2142cdff24ecdb89284503c5c16bb53c7db9852f86ce&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1226lFZE4ZS8TQgt4RMdTAPQ&amp;key=84e1ab98e194bf2dd3812086027a6de9bc46315d70182c553b3f9b1a440360451c4b3884f8caca92560ebebaa983ada81a203b37192498f03c9734d95d45cebaffb52f5ffba691ed7fe455dfdc3c96e1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=2Qmo8pivAuR0lUV1kSfH0irOSgbxmbcrsjKD76MADYvqxtFG94bdK0Ke5jDy1LIN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>蔚来圣诞节推出“光影圣诞” campaign，</b></a>为获奖者送上由礼品快递盒改造的“光影万花筒”，实际上是个投影仪，手动营造圣诞氛围。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0816fi4nn4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"wUdk\">蔚来还将投影仪放大，带到了太古汇 NIO House，在线下也上演了一场“圣诞光影秀”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k08170inqtd\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"mVrh\">MINI 中国和公益领养组织“北京领养日”发起<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320856224666969?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <b>“MINIPETLOVER” 活动</b></a>，邀请摄影师“纳纳酱 NANA”为待领养的小动物拍摄了写真，背景则是 MINI 的后备箱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115505ehIfZU3oNld7kYAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115507Aoy5af7prtvSJ6RV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.001000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115508cn9KlSp4DmY3BH58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.001000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115511hKGIHV2qnRMSpT3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"q1ID\">微信公众号后台编辑器改版，对新手来说体验度更好了。</p><p line=\"aSu4\">将顶部和右侧的菜单栏合并，同时颜色加深，能够更快更准确找到想使用的功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812261154191jDlGYTridExI9Kf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.270774\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"PGeI\">底部封面和摘要合并后，还能将部分功能选项隐藏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115429TwAiMxdOQLI0CGfu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"0qRX\">整个风格像最近的微信大升级一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226115440RwkI0h31P2iyXrMs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.484733\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"uHys\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/12/cardi-b-super-bowl-53-protest-colin-kaepernick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Cardi B 表示拒绝参加超级碗中场秀，</b></a>和 Rihanna 一样为支持 NFL 运动员 Colin Kaepernic。</p><p line=\"89lz\">爱奇艺之前披露的第三季财报显示，<b><a href=\"http://www.iqiyi.com/common/20181031/b662235fb79fa1c1.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">会员业务首次超过广告业务收入</a>，</b>占总营收比例 41% 。</p><p line=\"89lz\" class=\"\"><br></p><p line=\"89lz\" class=\"\">题图来自：Unsplash@Jonathan Daniels</p>"}